# Page Template: Detail Page

> Reference template for building single-entity detail pages in {{ display_name }}.

## Purpose

Detail pages display comprehensive information about a single entity (user, project, order, etc.) and provide actions to manage it.

## Layout Structure

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Header / Navigation Bar                          │
├──────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┤
│          │  Breadcrumb: Home > List > Entity Name │
│          ├───────────────────────────────────────┤
│          │  Entity Title          [Edit] [Delete] │
│          │  Status Badge / Subtitle               │
│  Sidebar ├───────────────────────────────────────┤
│          │  Tab Bar: Overview | Activity | Settings│
│  (nav)   ├───────────────────────────────────────┤
│          │  Tab Content Area                       │
│          │                                         │
│          │  Section 1: Key Information             │
│          │  ┌─────────────┬─────────────────┐     │
│          │  │ Field Label │ Value            │     │
│          │  │ Field Label │ Value            │     │
│          │  └─────────────┴─────────────────┘     │
│          │                                         │
│          │  Section 2: Related Items               │
│          │  ┌───────────────────────────────┐     │
│          │  │ Related item list / table      │     │
│          │  └───────────────────────────────┘     │
└──────────┴───────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Components

### Entity Header

- Entity name / title (large, prominent)
- Status badge (active, pending, archived)
- Primary actions: Edit, Delete, or domain-specific actions
- Secondary actions in a "..." dropdown menu

### Tab Navigation

- **Overview**: key information and metadata
- **Activity**: timeline of changes and events
- **Settings**: entity-specific configuration (if applicable)

### Key Information Section

- Label-value pairs in a 2-column grid
- Group related fields into subsections
- Show "-" for empty optional fields

### Related Items Section

- Table or card list of associated entities
- Link to each related entity's detail page
- "Add" action to create new relations

## States

| State | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| Loading | Skeleton for header and content |
| Not Found | 404 message with back link |
| Error | Error banner with retry |
| Loaded | Full entity display |
| Deleting | Confirmation modal before delete |

## Design Notes ({{ design_style }})

{% if design_style == "minimal-clean" %}
- Clean white card with subtle section separators
- Status badges use muted color fills
- Actions are text buttons, not prominent
{% elif design_style == "corporate-professional" %}
- Structured header with clear hierarchy
- Bordered sections with subtle backgrounds
- Actions are standard buttons with icons
{% elif design_style == "playful-modern" %}
- Colorful status badges and icons
- Rounded sections with light shadows
- Actions have hover animations
{% endif %}

## Data Requirements

- Endpoint: `GET /api/<entity>/:id`
- Activity: `GET /api/<entity>/:id/activity`
- Related: `GET /api/<entity>/:id/related`

## Accessibility

- Breadcrumb uses proper `nav` and `aria-label`
- Tabs use `role="tablist"` / `role="tab"` / `role="tabpanel"`
- Delete action requires confirmation
- Status badges have text labels, not just color
